&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/details&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that in the blog workflow below, you need to replace &lt;code&gt;feed_list&lt;/code&gt; with your own blog RSS address.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;If you are also using Hugo and the theme is Stack, the RSS address should be &lt;code&gt;https://your blog address/index.xml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
